CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 24, 1945, pg. 3, reads: "Seaman and Parents - Seaman Clarence Carpenter Jr., now stationed at a Naval Armory at Chicago, is pictured with his parents, Mr. and Mrs. Clarence Carpenter, of 2220 Wylie Avenue. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Clarence Carpenter Sr., Clarence Carpenter Jr. in US Navy sailor uniform, and Mrs. Carpenter posed in front of light colored background, in Harris Studio
